NAME
    Mirror::URI - Mirror Configuration and Auto-Discovery

DESCRIPTION
    Mirror::URI is an abstract base class for the mirror auto-discovery
    modules Mirror::YAML and Mirror::JSON.

    See their documentation for more details.

SUPPORT
    Bugs should be reported via the CPAN bug tracker at

    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Mirror-URI>

    For other issues, or commercial enhancement or support, contact the
    author.

AUTHOR
    Adam Kennedy <adamk@cpan.org>

SEE ALSO
    Mirror::YAML, Mirror::JSON, Mirror::CPAN

